Enum OperatorType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<OperatorType>
      • org.educraft.item.OperatorType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<OperatorType>

    public enum OperatorType
extends java.lang.Enum<OperatorType>
    Describes the four types of arithmetic operator. Used to provide unlocalised names to MathematicalOperator, and also used when performing calculations.
